## üéØ About

The **AI Robot Spider Control System** is a sophisticated hexapod robot control platform built on the Freenove Big Hexapod Robot Kit. This project features a distributed architecture with a Windows GUI client and a Raspberry Pi-based robot controller, connected via REST API and WebSockets for real-time control and video streaming.

### üåü Why This Project?

- **Educational:** Learn robotics, computer vision, and distributed systems
- **Modular:** Clean separation between client and robot control
- **Extensible:** Built on Freenove base with custom enhancements
- **Real-time:** Live camera feed and responsive controls
- **Professional:** Production-ready code with proper architecture

---

## ‚ú® Features

### üéÆ Robot Control
- ‚úÖ **18 Servo Motors** - Precise control of 6 legs (3 servos per leg)
- ‚úÖ **Multiple Movement Modes:**
  - Forward/Backward walking
  - Left/Right turning
  - Sideways movement (crab walk)
  - Rotation in place
  - Custom gaits and patterns
- ‚úÖ **Speed Control** - Adjustable movement speed
- ‚úÖ **Emergency Stop** - Instant halt functionality
- ‚úÖ **Servo Calibration** - Fine-tune individual servo positions

### üìπ Computer Vision
- ‚úÖ **Live Camera Feed** - Real-time video streaming from robot
- ‚úÖ **HD Quality** - 1080p video capture
- ‚úÖ **Low Latency** - Optimized streaming for responsive control
- üîÑ **Object Detection** (Planned) - AI-powered object recognition
- üîÑ **Autonomous Navigation** (Planned) - Self-driving capabilities

### üñ•Ô∏è Windows Client (PyQt5)
- ‚úÖ **Modern GUI** - Beautiful, responsive interface
- ‚úÖ **6 Custom Themes:**
  - VS Code Dark (default)
  - Dark Spider (classic black/purple)
  - Toxic Spider (neon green)
  - Halloween Spider (orange/black)
  - Blood Spider (red/black)
  - Caution Spider (yellow/black)
- ‚úÖ **Real-time Controls** - Keyboard and button controls
- ‚úÖ **Status Monitoring** - Connection status, battery level, servo states
- ‚úÖ **Camera View** - Live video feed display
- ‚úÖ **Settings Panel** - Customize robot behavior

### üåê Backend API (FastAPI)
- ‚úÖ **REST API** - Clean, documented endpoints
- ‚úÖ **WebSocket Support** - Real-time bidirectional communication
- ‚úÖ **Auto Documentation** - Swagger UI and ReDoc
- ‚úÖ **Error Handling** - Robust error management
- ‚úÖ **CORS Support** - Cross-origin requests enabled
- ‚úÖ **Health Checks** - System status monitoring

---

