### **Communication Flow**

```
User Input (Keyboard/Button)
        ‚Üì
PyQt5 GUI (Windows Client)
        ‚Üì
HTTP Request / WebSocket Message
        ‚Üì
FastAPI Server (Raspberry Pi)
        ‚Üì
Robot Control Logic
        ‚Üì
Freenove Base Code
        ‚Üì
PCA9685 PWM Driver
        ‚Üì
18 Servo Motors
        ‚Üì
Robot Movement! üï∑Ô∏è
```

