## üîß Hardware

### **Components**

| Component | Specification | Purpose |
|-----------|--------------|---------|
| **Raspberry Pi 5** | 4GB RAM, Debian Trixie | Main controller |
| **Freenove Hexapod Kit** | 18 servo motors | Robot chassis & actuators |
| **PCA9685** | 16-channel PWM driver | Servo control |
| **Camera Module** | 1080p, CSI interface | Video streaming |
| **Battery** | 7.4V 2S LiPo, 2200mAh | Power supply |
| **Servo Motors** | MG90S, 180¬∞ rotation | Leg movement |

### **Wiring Diagram**

```
Raspberry Pi 5
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ I2C (SDA/SCL) ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí PCA9685 (Servo Driver)
    ‚îÇ                      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Channel 0-2  ‚Üí Leg 1 (Hip, Knee, Ankle)
    ‚îÇ                      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Channel 3-5  ‚Üí Leg 2
    ‚îÇ                      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Channel 6-8  ‚Üí Leg 3
    ‚îÇ                      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Channel 9-11 ‚Üí Leg 4
    ‚îÇ                      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Channel 12-14 ‚Üí Leg 5
    ‚îÇ                      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Channel 15-17 ‚Üí Leg 6
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ CSI Port ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí Camera Module
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ GPIO ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí LEDs, Sensors (future)
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Power ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí 5V from Battery (via regulator)
```

